description.en: MadnessFM is a 24/7 online radio station, based in the UK. We have been around for almost a year and love bringing you the greatest hits! We also have a golden oldies station as well. This radio station is brought to you by Kane Productions!
description.ga_IE: Is stáisiún raidió 24/7 ar líne é MadnessFM, atá lonnaithe sa Ríocht Aontaithe.Táimid tar éis a bheith thart ar feadh beagnach bliain agus grá a thabhairt duit na amas is mó!Tá stáisiún Oldies Golden againn chomh maith.Tugtar Kane Productions an stáisiún raidió seo chugat!
